{"featured_counts":2,"common_counts":51,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/562997756/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=7\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/562997756/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=5\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":22},"data":[{"id":567888537,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567888537","content":"评论区太善良了，真的，我说的是，太善良了。\u003cbr\u003e但有些善良，是会起反作用的。\u003cbr\u003e为一人，诛天下人之心，这样的善良其实是恶。\u003cbr\u003e对题主这样装睡的人。\u003cbr\u003e没必要站在世界中心呼唤爱了。\u003cbr\u003e一个高中生说他要学好编程，做出世界上最好玩的游戏，这个值得鼓励，值得爱。\u003cbr\u003e一个初中生说他要写出一篇小说，让所有人喜欢，这个值得鼓励，值得爱。\u003cbr\u003e一个高中生，说他证明出来了哥德巴赫猜想，要靠这个上清华北大。\u003cbr\u003e抱歉，这个不值得鼓励，不值得爱，是bullshit，是对潜心数学研究，默默无闻的科研工作者的侮辱。\u003cbr\u003e好比一个人指着爆炸的挑战者号航天飞机，说，航天飞机失事是与当年点火时的火柴有关，加热发射器的木炭品质用错了，1月1号，我公布它失事的真正原因。\u003cbr\u003e这是对为科学献身的先辈们的亵渎。\u003cbr\u003e这样的人，以这样一个傲慢无礼的姿态出现在这样一个严肃的话题下，还能如此道貌岸然，这是让真正的学者无奈而寒心的。\u003cbr\u003e我承认，天才与疯子，往往只有一线之隔。\u003cbr\u003e但这不代表，一个人，装疯卖傻，他就真的有可能是天才了。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546175622,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"89451b5e351a23ab21b2c9fcc6218ab9","url_token":"mu-yu-59-38","name":"木雨","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a8f60fac4f2dccc134ef51c3f2528aa3_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a8f60fac4f2dccc134ef51c3f2528aa3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/89451b5e351a23ab21b2c9fcc621